@PhotonCap Thanks! I know a some followers recommended Aixtorn, but there's other interesting suppliers like Oxford Instruments out there. 

I already did more DD into $IQE and the epiwafer merchant foundries, but there's the $ASML's of the photonics world too. 

Surprisingly $VECO was up there too although I knew them for HBM related stuff.

@Mellokhai Riber is also very interesting if you like $VECO and want quantum exposure.

Rare as well to have a hyperscaler like $MSFT as your main customer, trades at 27 p/e, and is profitable.

Quantum dot lasers are a little early though…
